spec_data.Name: emacs-proofgeneral-el
spec_data.Description:
This package contains the elisp source files for Proof General under
GNU Emacs. You do not need to install this package to run Proof
General. Install the emacs-proofgeneral package to use Proof General with
GNU Emacs.
